Miss, you'll lose your hat.

119
00:14:07,805 --> 00:14:08,888
Don't worry, Kinu.

120
00:14:17,606 --> 00:14:18,898
Watch out!

121
00:14:22,236 --> 00:14:23,236
Are you all right?

122
00:14:23,487 --> 00:14:25,029
Safe!

123
00:14:25,531 --> 00:14:26,864
Nice play.

124
00:14:27,908 --> 00:14:28,950
Thank you.

